HOWTO irssi:
https://irssi.org

Start the program:
irssi <options> <url> <port>

Navigate servers:
/connect, /join, /leave, /nick

Secure nick inside server:
/msg NickServ HELP

Query channels:
/msg Alis LIST <query>

List of @chat commands:
https://pastebin.com/raw/sRaG51VD

OPTIONS (irssi):

-tls			  : Enables TLS.


HOWTO oathtool:

Retrieve the key:
pass github.2fa

Get the code:
oathtool -b --totp "<key>"


HOWTO neomutt:

Mark email for deletion:
<d>

Sync changes with server:
<$>



HOWTO pass:

Get password:
pass <name>

Store password:
pass insert <name>

List passwords:
pass list



HOWTO ranger:

Start program:
ranger

-Arrow keys to move around.
-Space to select file/directory.

:mkdir / :touch		- Create directory/file(s).
:delete				- Delete directory/file(s).



HOWTO xterm:

Copy Text:
Shift+PrtSc OR Right click

Paste Text:
Shift+Insert OR Middle click
